def productExceptSelf(nums):
    length = len(nums)
    ans = [1] / length
    (left, right) = (1, 1)
    for i in range(length):
        ans[i] *= left
        ans[length - i - 1] *= right
        left *= nums[i]
        right *= nums[length - i - 1]
    return ans
